  "texts": [
    "While AI offers promising opportunities to enhance learning experiences, concerns regarding its potential overhype also exist.",
    "GenAI in EducationAI chatbots are becoming valuable tools in education, aiding teachers in their preparation and students in their learning journeys.",
    "Incorporating GenAI into educational settings signifies a significant shift in teaching and learning methodologies.",
    "The widespread use of GenAI in education introduces ethical dilemmas and practical challenges, particularly concerning authenticity, plagiarism, and their impact on learning outcomes.",
    "It is essential to address these concerns to leverage GenAI's advantages while minimizing its risks [9].The quality of classroom discourse is vital for effective learning, and emerging technologies such as GenAI offer new ways to enhance educational experiences [10]; [11]; [12]."
